20011228, prboom-2.2.2, kongar

- rewrote the last line of BUILD. Std. unpack function is not
  capable of handling .wad.gz files, gunzip -c is used instead.

- the name of the wad file is changed from doom-1.8.wad to
  doom1.wad. Prboom is not capable of handling more then
  one dot in the filename.
